==English==

===Adjective===
'''outer'''
# Outside; [[external]].
# Further from the centre of the inside.

====Translations====
*German: [[äußere]]
*Swedish: [[yttre]] (1)
*Telugu: [[బహిర్గత]] (bahirgata) (1, 2), [[బాహ్య]] (baahya) (1, 2)

===Noun===
'''outer'''
# An outer part.
# ([[wholesale]] [[trade]]) the smallest single [[unit]] normally sold to [[retailer]]s, usually equal to one retail [[display]] box.
#:We ordered two [[carton]]s with twelve '''outers''' in each.
